  "slug": "chocolate-chip-cookies",
  "title": "Chocolate chip cookies",
  "subtitle": "American-style: crisp edge, soft centre",
  "excerpt": "Twenty-four cookies with crisp, slightly browned edges and a soft, fudgy centre. Brown butter and extra yolk give more flavour than the basic recipe; resting the dough overnight deepens the chocolate.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "The American chocolate chip cookie derives from the Toll House recipe (1930s). The brown-butter technique is documented in mid-twentieth-century American baking literature. This recipe follows the standard US home-baking formula adapted for British ingredients: plain flour in place of all-purpose, caster sugar in place of granulated, dark chocolate chips.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The basic American cookie formula works. The version here makes two small changes: brown the butter, and add an extra egg yolk. Both moves are about flavour. The ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "brown butter",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpa6epvu0000s0v4ynz1fey1"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " adds a toasty, almost caramel note that plain melted butter cannot. The extra yolk adds richness without making the cookie cakey.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "One American cup of all-purpose flour is approximately 125 g. This recipe uses 280 g of plain flour, the British equivalent of 2¼ cups.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "ingredientsGroup",
            "attrs": {
              "title": null
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "unsalted-butter",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 225,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "dark-brown-sugar",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 200,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "caster-sugar",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 100,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "free-range-eggs",
                  "unit": null,
                  "prepNote": "1 whole egg + 1 extra yolk",
                  "quantity": 2,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "vanilla-extract",
                  "unit": "tsp",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 2,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
